Method():

· Method is a block of code, it contains set of statement and it perform some specific task.

· It also perform specific task without retyping the code.

· Method is used to represent behavior of object.

· It is also used to achieve the reusability of code.

· A method will not execute directly, if we want to execute method we have to call that explicitly.

· The main method should call to each and every method to execute.